{"tid":1924170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全中國 Apple Store 今天已重開　意大利全國暫停","createTime":"2020-03-13T13:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T13:59:31.000Z","uid":66365,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ff189010e7d02584b28487e35c4ebc517d2c89cd","tid":1924170,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:51:54.000Z","msg":"因疫情影響，二月初 Apple 將全中國的 Apple Store 也暫停，隨著近期中國疫情改善，已陸續將一些地區的 Apple Store 重開。本周較早前，全中國 42 間 Apple Store 有 38 間亦已重新，而今天 Apple 已將 42 間 Apple Store 重開。<br />\n<br />\n不過，意大利 Apple Store 已暫停，而隨著其他地區的疫情惡化，相信全球 Apple Store 也開始受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇黎大陸真係爆完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c71d6727691a752d055e1b339c807bb6614d20a","tid":1924170,"uid":74171,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:53:22.000Z","msg":"爆完？<br />\n疫情<em>新聞</em>已受控咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82562f2bda371ec28b9c49c36b7c2fc61d5a9721","tid":1924170,"uid":34525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"開始分唔到中國到底係點"},{"pid":"5493241007c205a9b78665083e023994c9ebb190","tid":1924170,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"係咪爆完就未知 , 習種好急於宣佈戰勝疫症就肯定"},{"pid":"012dd968631e018a00a9d7b05bf22387e65eac50","tid":1924170,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:55:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔仲要呃自己呃到幾時"},{"pid":"64e17a0c3ad2b723d39065ce5d65953a9631e48f","tid":1924170,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5493241007c205a9b78665083e023994c9ebb190","tid":1924170,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"係咪爆完就未知 , 習種好急於宣佈戰勝疫症就肯定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T13:56:30.000Z",